opinions.text:
Opinion by
Mr. Justice Mestrezat,
For the reasons given in the opinion handed down herewith in the case of Henry C. Frick and others against the United Firemen’s Insurance Company, No. 21, January Term, 1907, 218 Pa. 409, the judgment of the court below is affirmed.
